I. ABOUT THE PROJECT
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




II. REQUIREMENTS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following software is required to build and run the avida-macos viewer project:

 - Avida (core and viewer-core libraries) 2.13 latest git repository snapshot (git://avida.devosoft.org/avida.git)
 - Apple Mac OS X 10.6.6 or greater
 - Apple Xcode 4.0 or greater


Additional software needed to contribute to the project:

 - Git 1.7 or greater


